OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRain in the
OL,6,Fwest will soon spread to all parts
OL,7,Fthrough the evening, becoming heavy
OL,8,Ffor a time before clearing before
OL,9,Fdawn, followed by clear spells and
OL,10,Fblustery showers.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FBright spells and blustery
OL,13,Fshowers at first. Drier for a time in
OL,14,Fthe middle of the day before further
OL,15,Fshowers later, heavy at times. Cool
OL,16,Fand blustery.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
