OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FRather
OL,6,Fcold and unsettled Wednesday with
OL,7,Fscattered heavy showers, the showers
OL,8,Fdying out through Thursday evening.
OL,9,FChance of overnight frosts. Mostly dry
OL,10,Fon Friday with sunny spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
